    "description": {
      "value": "<p>You create a burst of glorious, glowing golden feathers centered on a point you choose within range. Each friendly creature in the burst regains 4d6 hit points and is no longer charmed or frightened, if it suffered those conditions. Each hostile creature in the burst must make a Wisdom saving throw. On a failed save, a creature takes 4d6 radiant damage and is blinded until the end of its next turn. On a successful save, a creature takes half the damage and isnâ€™t blinded.<br><em><strong>At Higher Levels.</strong></em> When you cast this spell using a spell slot of 7th level or higher, the healing and damage both increase by 1d6 for each slot level above 6th.<br>Content licensed under the @UUID[Compendium.koboldpressogl.koboldpressjournal.JournalEntry.KoboldPressOGL00.JournalEntryPage.KoboldPressOGLpg]{Open Game License}",
